cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Atlantia Empire in your research or build on it, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Atlantia Empire"
abstract: >
  Atlantia Empire is a constitutional governance platform for large multi-agent AI systems.
  It wraps 261 domain-specialist AI personas in an 8-article written constitution, a standing
  judicial branch that reviews every deliverable before it ships, role-based access control,
  budget enforcement, memory tiering, and an evaluation harness — so orchestrating a swarm of
  AI agents does not also mean scaling risk, unreviewed output, and untracked cost.
